'''Iron Will''' was the official feed of the [[Commission for the Preservation of the New Order/Legends|Commission for the Preservation of the New Order]]. All COMPNOR members were given a free subscription and exclusive access to breaking news reports. New members received a special welcome message from [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] himself.

